Cell["\<\
Exercise 1 : Conceptual questions  on data science and data structures \
[Chapters 1 and 2, TB by Shah]\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811597523431114*^9, 3.811597554184411*^9}, {
  3.811598863166101*^9, 3.811598863630541*^9}, {3.811598972411062*^9, 
  3.81159902004309*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cd8303ff-9ad4-4272-8f87-\
6aee558f2e19"],

Cell["\<\
What is data science? How does it relate to and differ from statistics?\
\>", "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811597558054982*^9, 3.8115976057370243`*^9}, {
  3.811598866902531*^9, 
  3.811598885346279*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a04b0c87-b27a-4c7c-9818-\
9acb7afeb878"],

Cell["\<\
Data science is an evolving and dynamic multidisciplinary field, with several \
incipient definitions. But they have in common that it is aimed at \
understanding a phenomenon or a problem based on data. Several tools and \
techniques are used, drawn from several areas of science. Out of the several \
definitions laid by our lecturer, I like most the one from ... because ...! \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811917878316254*^9, 3.8119178920556097`*^9}, {
  3.811917934086451*^9, 3.811918035375775*^9}, {3.811920588127755*^9, 
  3.811920590877549*^9}, {3.905232054308705*^9, 3.905232058985454*^9}, {
  3.905232281629093*^9, 
  3.905232286917364*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e1448bac-972d-4ff6-b26f-\
847627bf7ddb"],

Cell["\<\
According to Shah, statistics provides a powerful way to prepare, explore and \
construct statistical models of data. Data science allows statistical tools \
and approaches to be used to large and  heterogeneous datasets. But it offers \
also other techniques and approaches of analysis.

Both data science and statistics involve the analysis of data to uncover \
patterns and insights.

Data science is a broader field that encompasses various aspects of data \
analysis, including data collection, data cleaning, machine learning, and \
data engineering.

Statistics focuses primarily on data analysis, hypothesis testing, and \
probability theory.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811920568389354*^9, 3.811920582461233*^9}, {
  3.905232124203065*^9, 3.905232125964708*^9}, {3.905232159987457*^9, 
  3.90523218739465*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a9cdc7c5-7325-49aa-8c23-\
2ff22e2fd7ab"],

Cell["\<\
Identify three areas or domains in which data science is being used and \
describe how.\
\>", "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811597558054982*^9, 3.8115976057370243`*^9}, {
  3.811598866902531*^9, 
  3.811598906759768*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4a67ec1d-fb1f-4167-bc97-\
c16f39e03a12"],

Cell["\<\
In addition to the areas already described on the lecture, I can identify \
other areas such as\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811919339920164*^9, 3.811919487235014*^9}, {
  3.8119195462493978`*^9, 
  3.811919563040159*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2ad4a3d2-a554-44b7-aa93-\
55f753c889c6"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["farming",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ", where the farm can use satellite images to analyse soil characteristics \
to help determine quantity of fertilizer and pesticide needed over a \
particular area (precision agriculture), helping the environment, i.e. making \
sure that you do not use too much pesticide, also stop excess run-off of both \
fertilizers and pesticides into ground water, determine a router plan to plan \
different crops in a specific area. "
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811919339920164*^9, 3.811919487235014*^9}, {
  3.8119195462493978`*^9, 3.8119195873670893`*^9}, {3.811919619288604*^9, 
  3.811919639263153*^9}, {3.8119197575282993`*^9, 3.8119197575298347`*^9}, {
  3.946719789075673*^9, 
  3.946719846850994*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c7d44a9d-966b-49f0-95be-\
2e5e31242cf9"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Demand prediction for the manufacturing industry",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ": One of our colleagues is now the data scientists of a large pharma \
company and they are responsible for predicting the future sales of products. \
The report produced about these sales triggers all decisions in the company \
regarding the production, storage and distribution of their products. \
Prediction is done using the same AI/machine learning techniques you will be \
using in this course. "
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811919339920164*^9, 3.811919487235014*^9}, {
   3.8119195462493978`*^9, 3.8119195873670893`*^9}, {3.811919619288604*^9, 
   3.811919639263153*^9}, 3.811919758321819*^9, {3.811919794547084*^9, 
   3.811919834048593*^9}, {3.873965563817114*^9, 3.873965705783808*^9}, {
   3.8747290102437563`*^9, 3.874729012329845*^9}, 
   3.883631844503295*^9},ExpressionUUID->"b65e9c92-fc5d-4f3d-8a8c-\
9ff890b5d02d"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Automation in space exploration [",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["Cosmic",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://www.zooniverse.org/projects/wkiri/cosmic/about/research"], 
    None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://www.zooniverse.org/projects/wkiri/cosmic/about/research"],
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 StyleBox["]",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ": One of the challenges in space exploration is the extremely small amount \
of data that can be sent between Earth and a distant spacecraft. Because \
keeping humans alive in space is so expensive and difficult, most space \
missions are in effect highly specialized robots. Machine learning is being \
used to help determine what should be sent home: \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Do \
the images look reasonable?\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Which ten images are the important ones to send to \
Earth?\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]What surprising changes \
or new findings did you observe?\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]"
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811919339920164*^9, 3.811919487235014*^9}, {
  3.8119195462493978`*^9, 3.8119195873670893`*^9}, {3.811919619288604*^9, 
  3.811919636482476*^9}, {3.811919861028764*^9, 3.811919889452607*^9}, {
  3.811920231697721*^9, 3.811920238009261*^9}, {3.811920278157941*^9, 
  3.811920314832438*^9}, {3.811920376364506*^9, 
  3.811920407926022*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"421e212f-7951-4ed0-938d-\
c26138ce276a"],

