Cell[TextData[StyleBox["For your second option, you can make cake with the \
same ingredients. However, the ratio of the ingredients being different, it \
will cost you $4 per lb. The initial setup cost is $2000, while the labour \
charge remains the same. However, baking two batches of cake will require 3 \
hours in total, with five cakes in each batch. Each cake when baked with 2 lb \
of ingredient can be sold at $34. ",
 FontSize->24,
 FontWeight->"Regular"]], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811598090828949*^9, 3.81159812479241*^9}, {
