Cell["Notice : ", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811927958925064*^9, 
  3.8119279620511847`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ae1619af-2eaa-4989-a3ab-\
f3a3a9fa86b3"],

Cell["\<\
When deciding for what to show in the Table, you have done in your brain a \
database model.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811927967375921*^9, 
  3.811927991092507*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"901a66da-3fe9-4c3d-b244-\
827ef3c4c756"],

Cell["\<\
You will see that not all the data needs to be shown. Also, not all data is \
required for the calculations (the ingredients for example).\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811927967375921*^9, 3.811928011158197*^9}, {
  3.811928091621874*^9, 3.811928091622552*^9}, {3.811928774145267*^9, 
  3.811928787329019*^9}, {3.90523165588721*^9, 
  3.905231655889233*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f0ecbcc1-5508-4762-b0c4-\
b0e4d4d3a789"],

Cell["This calculation assumes that all that is produced is sold.", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811927967375921*^9, 3.811928011158197*^9}, {
  3.811928091621874*^9, 3.811928091622552*^9}, {3.811928774145267*^9, 
  3.811928787329019*^9}, {3.905231656588334*^9, 
  3.905231675627476*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4005b59e-9f96-4b95-bbbb-\
37c032d60dca"],

Cell["\<\
You need to decide about costs and incomes per a time unit, that can be used \
to any product, which I decided per hour. But you could have decided for the \
amount of hours that the baker works to prepare the products.  \
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811927967375921*^9, 3.811928011158197*^9}, {
  3.811928092528615*^9, 3.811928133096579*^9}, {3.811931481128299*^9, 
  3.811931534972011*^9}, {3.905231411510869*^9, 
  3.905231411512435*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3e676c57-fc06-4618-9dac-\
7a12db9f14a4"],

Cell["\<\
ChatGPT 3.5 has wrongly calculated the income per hour in the second (cakes) \
and third (bagels) exercises.  \
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811927967375921*^9, 3.811928011158197*^9}, {
  3.811928092528615*^9, 3.811928133096579*^9}, {3.811931481128299*^9, 
  3.811931534972011*^9}, {3.905231414056597*^9, 
  3.905231482118291*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"17f13691-ae33-4733-94e9-\
691c629c566c"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
